caption: My Trailer drops tomorrow for my new film #ambulancemovies

He taught me so much.  Sean the legend.  To me, and so many others.  My very first line of direction I was actually afraid to ask...“Sean can you please say that less charming”. He said, “sure boy”. That’s what he called me the whole movie, ‘boy’. I was just a kid, directing him in ‘The Rock’. Sean,  you taught me more then you will ever know.  To this day, you gruffly taking me under your wing Is still in everything I do.  Rest In Peace my friend. @seanconnery_official @seanconnerydaily
Ryan Reynolds and I just wrapped up a fun one. Last shot.

We call this on my set. “One man, one man alone”.
This is me shooting In Abu Dhabi.
Blast from the past. NASA shuttle launchpad. I’m the only director to ever be allowed to ever shoot not 1, but 2 movies out on this special place.

Filming in front of the last shuttle to ever launch at NASA.
Today is a big day for NASA launching their new rocket. Yes private industry helped make this possible. But there is nothing like the sophisticated massive tech of NASA getting these rockets successfully in space.
Tight squeeze shooting in this car.
Me and Pitbull.  We just finished working together.  Ok I’m wearing my sweatpants. I was operating camera all day @pitbull

The last shot!  Finished my new movie posing with some of my GREAT camera brothers.  Yes we took our masks off for this shot, but we’ve been tested tested tested tested so save your whining for someone else. We just wanted a picture we could remember.
